com.sponsorpay.publisher.interstitial

Interface SPInterstitialRequestListener


  • public interface SPInterstitialRequestListener
    Interface to be implemented by listeners notified of the results of an Interstitial request.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onSPInterstitialAdAvailable(android.content.Intent interstitialActivity)
      Invoked when an ad is available for this request.
      void onSPInterstitialAdError(java.lang.String errorMessage)
      Invoked when the request results in a local error, usually due to a problem connecting to the network.
      void onSPInterstitialAdNotAvailable()
      Invoked when the back end cannot provide any ad for this request.
